originalText.text: It was an absolute pleasure choosing Skyluxe Group to take on our kitchen renovation. I‚Äôm so grateful for the great work they did and their punctual delivery to completion. Their craftsmanship and patience with our particular requests was unlike anything I have seen. They would genuinely listen to our requests and implement them. My wife and I just moved into our first home in October and were eager to get our renovations done in time to host Thanksgiving. At first, we were accepting of the possibility that it may not be done in time. When I shared my concerns with the owner, Suad, he promised that he would make arrangements to get it done in time. Honestly I was surprised because our request was a little unreasonable due to the time crunch. He was adamant about coming through for us and had his team worked everyday until the project was done. We hosted Thanksgiving this year and were able to enjoy our new kitchen in time for the holiday!! Thank you so much Suad and Skyluxe!! We appreciate your diligence and keeping your promise. I highly recommend them to anyone looking to renovate their home. They genuinely cared about our home like it was theirs. The craftsmanship was amazing, they listen to every detail to bring our vision to fruition and they were so friendly and polite. Thank you again Skyluxe!! Check out our new kitchen!
